 <name>PEAR2_HTTP_Request</name>
 <channel>pear2.php.net</channel>
 <summary>class to do http requests, uses a adapter based system for performing those requests
</summary>
 <description>
Please see the examples dir for basic usage

Adapters are available for based on the following code and are used in this order:
PEAR2_HTTP_Request_Adapter_Http (uses the Pecl Http class)
PEAR2_HTTP_Request_Adapter_Curl (based on the curl extension, not complete)
PEAR2_HTTP_Request_Adapter_Phpstream (based on the http php stream code)
PEAR2_HTTP_Request_Adapter_Phpsocket (based on php sockets, built from PEAR1 HTTP_Request)
</description>
